dc_description_s: This line data layer represents transportation features for the Dane County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Dane_MPO_Transportation_2016.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are FixedGuideWay, FutureFuncClass, ParkRide, Ped_Path, Rail, RoadsCurrent, and RoadsPlanned. These layers can be used in conjunction with the MPO bike paths/facilities dataset.
dc_creator_sm: City of Madison - Metropolitan Planning Organization (MPO)
